# Focus App — Cursor rules (MVP 1)

- Always use Next.js 15 App Router conventions.
- Use React Server Components by default for data fetching.
- Only use 'use client' for: MediaRecorder, useState, useRef, timer logic.
- NEVER use @supabase/auth-helpers — always use @supabase/ssr.
- NEVER use setInterval for timers — always use Date.now() delta.
- All time tracking must use session_events table.
- Wrap all Claude API responses in Zod schemas.
- Always validate Supabase ops with try/catch.
